Script,Gambling3N
setDealerCode(`

produce 100
dealer south

# Gambling 3N
hcp(south)>8 and hcp(south)<12  // could have a Q or two J's outside
and
(
(top3(south,diamonds)==3 and diamonds(south)>6)
or
(top3(south,clubs)==3 and clubs(south)>6)
)

`,"S",true)
Script
Button,Gambling 3N,--- Gambling 3N\n\
A gambling 3N opening bid shows a solid 7+-card minor suit and less than a K outside.\n\
%Gambling3N%
